    <ThingDef ParentName="BodyPartStandardMechadendriteBase">
        <defName>Marak_StandardMechadendrite</defName>
        <label>standard mechadendrite</label>
        <description>A standard mechadendrite fabricated using modern techniques. The addition of mini-servos gives it impeccable movement while a flexible shell grants it exceptional flexibility. A biogel nerve-link wired into the wielder's spine allows for exquisite control and usability marking it the top of its class.</description>
